text: Jianshe (), derived from the Standard Mandarin pinyin 'Jiànshè' for the Chinese '建设/建設' may refer to the following locations in China: == Towns (建设镇) == *Jianshe, Chongming County, in Shanghai *Jianshe, Zigong County, in Sichuan *Jianshe, Sanzhi County, in Sichuan *Jianshe, Baiyü County, in Garze Tibetan Autonomous Prefecture, Sichuan *Jianshe, Datian County, in Fujian *Jianshe, Fuxin County, in Fuxin Mongol Autonomous County, Liaoning == Subdistricts (建设街道)== *Jianshe Subdistrict, Yakeshi, in Inner Mongolia *Jianshe Subdistrict, Jiaxing, in Nanhu District, Jiaxing, Zhejiang *Jianshe Subdistrict, Shangqiu, in Liangyuan District, Shangqiu, Henan *Jianshe Subdistrict, Zhuzhou, in Lusong District, Zhuzhou, Hunan *Jianshe Subdistrict, Guangzhou, in Yuexiu District, Guangzhou, Guangdong *Jianshe Subdistrict, Zhanjiang, in Xiashan District, Zhanjiang, Guangdong *Jianshe Subdistrict, Jiayuguan City, in Jiayuguan City, Gansu == Village (建设村) == *Liuji, Liuji, Dawu County, Xiaogan, Hubei
title: Jianshe
